name: Candice Swanepoel
description:
A request of @tkpw.

Candice Swanepoel is a South African supermodel, selected by the Maxim magazine as the sexiest woman in the world in 2014.

1500-step TI trained on a dataset of 20 images with my usual settings (reducing the learning rate to 0.001 after step 1000).

Curious about my work process? I have summarized it here.

Appreciate my work? My TIs are free, but you can always buy me a coffee. :)
